Swiss Franc Surgest to Highest Level In At Least 40 Years Versus Dollar

-- B y   K e i t h   C a m p b e l l
-- 
2011-04-21T07:59:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-21/swiss-franc-surgest-to-highest-level-in-at-least-40-years-versus-dollar.html
The Swiss franc surged to its
highest level against the dollar since at least 1971, when
Bloomberg records begin.  The franc appreciated 0.6 percent to 88.24 centimes per 
dollar as of 8:55 a.m. in  London . The Swiss currency 
surpassed its previous 40-year peak against the greenback, 
reached on March 17.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Keith Campbell at 
 k.campbell@bloomberg.net  